songs.lyrics:
Lyrics from Snippet

[Verse]
Nigga, this is the day of the week I get it (Uh-huh)
And if a lil' freak seen out with me, you can guarantee I hit it (Let's go)
I'ma pull up with thirty-five women (Three), need to see ID, I'm big (I can't pick)
Ballin' like the NBA, they keep the NBA, they wanna hang out with me (Yeah, bitch)
Whatchu niggas know about playin' with me
Fuck bitches, get money, we Jay-Z and Penny
And I just got one hundred thousand on a show, that shit I was wearin' a piece (No cap)
I'm a hundred percent of the shit that I eat
Anyways...
songs.title: Hundred*
